0.3.5 2017-07-25

- Fix bug when PERL5LIB does not include `$project_root_dir/lib` for Perl stories
- Strun now changes to CWD by default ( unless --cwd is set )

0.3.4 2017-07-14

- Free style command line arguments documentation
- Single dashes parameters support

0.3.3 2017-07-13

* Auto coercion use `--` instead of `-` for options and flags

0.3.2 2017-07-13

* Auto coercion of `args` in configuration file to `cli_args`

0.3.1 2017-07-11

- Support for experimental feature - pass command line arguments in free style by ` -- args args args ` in `plg run` and `task run` commands

0.3.0 2017-07-10

- story check files are no longer mandatory ( yes, you can leave them! )
- meta stories no longer exist - instead we can talk just about story meta headers
- bash arrays support, thanks to @Spigell - https://github.com/melezhik/outthentic/pull/3
- huge improvements of documentation
- a lot of refactoring
- prettifying story headers in strun's reports ( I've made them more clear and meaningful )
- test_root_dir is deprecated in favor cache_root_dir

